===Pronunciation===
לחם / lechem / lekh'-em

===Etymology===
From לחם / lâcham  {{HH|3898}}; 

===Noun===
'''לחם'''

# Food (for man or beast), especially bread, or grain (for making it): - ([shew-]) bread, X eat, food, fruit, loaf, meat, victuals. 

